.Dd April 7, 2019
.Dt A34KBBC 4 amiga
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm a34kbbc
.Nd Amiga 3000/4000 on-board real-time clock
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "a34kbbc at mainbus0"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
real-time clock driver provides support for the Ricoh RP5C01 chip found
in A3000/A4000 class machines.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr todr 9
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device first appeared in
.Nx 1.3 .
